//activity_main2.xml This application has been developed in the context of a mobile phone project at our school the ESIEA. Its purpose is to show our capabilities to : - display some basic grafic elements (buttons, textview, pictures,edittext) and give them a use (changing the color, refreshing the date, changing a picture) - realise a portrait mode/landscape mode (as can be seen on the main page and the edittext page) - create many activities - implement services like notifications, toats ... - create an action bar and menus - create a JSON downloading service - add a link to another application (YouTube in our case) - convert automatically the text in the language of the device (effective for fr-rFR and en-rGB) - insert an action to quit FAGOT Arthur, PERRAULT William Students in the first cycle of engineering at the ESIEA, Paris, 2016
